There are five programs here:
1. A user should read the program written in the file "introductionsignal.c" first.
2. After that he should run the program "basicsignaldemo.c"
3. Next he should run the program "advancedsignaldemo.c"
4. "useofsignal.c" contains the program which should be read and executed next.
5. In the end, "cautionwithsignal.c" should be used.

Read the comments carefully provided at the top of the each file
Use the "makefile" to compile the programs.
